title: Grateful Dead Live at Bayfront Center Arena on 1988-10-15
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6MHz) > dBpoweramp > WAV (24-bit/96k)
description:
Set I
The Music Never Stopped
Sugaree
Blow Away
Walkin' Blues
When Push Comes To Shove
Queen Jane Approximately
Tennessee Jed
Let it Grow
Set II
One More Saturday Night

Uncle John's Band
Drums
Space
Truckin'
Smokestack Lightning
Stella Blue
Turn On Your Lovelight

Encore:
U.S. Blues

 
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
